          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1679046412786-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to a bowl with a large knob of <strong>butter </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>garlic & coriander butter</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1679046417060-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1679046417060-x400.jpg",
