          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1679046428764-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To make the perfect burrito, top each <strong>tortilla</strong> with some <strong>spinach</strong>, <strong>cardamom rice</strong> and <strong>butter chicken curry</strong>, fold the sides of each tortilla in and wrap the bottom of the tortilla over the filling, tucking it in tightly</p><p>Roll your <strong>tortilla </strong>until you’re left with a <strong>burrito </strong>– these are your <strong>butter chicken breast burritos</strong></p><p>Tip: Go light on the filling on your first one so that you don't overfill the burritos!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1679046431851-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1679046431851-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
