          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1679046431851-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>butter chicken breast burritos </strong>to the reserved baking tray[s] and put in the oven for 6-8 min or until lightly browned and crisp</p><p>Once browned, remove the tray[s] from the oven and spread the <strong>garlic & coriander butter</strong> over the burritos – these are your <strong>garlic & coriander butter chicken breast burritos</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
