            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>garlic & coriander butter chicken breast burritos </strong>in half and serve</p><p>Tip: Watch out for any cardamom pods!</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
